    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s high-revving pinnacle, featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain delivers a linear 333 hp to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefitting from reinforced subframe mounting points and a suspension setup that preserves the car\u2019s legendary 50/50 weight distribution and turn-in precision. While the exterior reflects honest road use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including rod bearing health and valve clearances\u2014have been kept within tight tolerances. This is an enthusiast-grade driver\u2019s car engineered for high-velocity apex hunting and visceral feedback.",
